title: Bluewater Design
description: Founded Bluewater Design in May 2022, a company that sells functional pieces of art. While active, Bluewater Design achived a large social media following and professional branding. Near the end of operations, Bluewater Design brought in rougly $6500 in revenue over a short period of time. The company was dissolved in Janurary 2023.

title: Project Here
description: Currently working on our Year 2 project, a automated work cell. This project has required us to design and build a work cell that can perform a task. The work cell is controlled by a PLC and has a HMI for user interaction.
